@page "/solutions/dry-goods"
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components

<PageTitle>Nuts & Dry Goods — DMD StockShopOnline</PageTitle>

<div class="sol-hero">
    <div class="sol-hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-left">
            <div class="sol-eyebrow">
                <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
                Built for bulk retail
            </div>
            <h1 class="sol-title">Selling by the gram<br /><span class="sol-accent">shouldn't mean guessing.</span></h1>
            <p class="sol-sub">Bulk and weight-based retail has always been tricky to manage — partial units, variable costs, and stock that's hard to count. DMD tracks it all precisely, so you always know what you have and what it's worth.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="/contact?plan=drygoods" class="btn-primary">Start free trial</a>
                <a href="/pricing" class="btn-ghost">See pricing</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-right">
            <div class="proof-card">
                <div class="proof-header">
                    <div class="proof-avatar amber-avatar">KH</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="proof-name">Karim H.</div>
                        <div class="proof-role">Owner, nuts &amp; spices shop · Ottawa</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="proof-quote">"We sell over 200 products by weight. DMD lets us track inventory in kilograms, set our own units, and the purchase order system means we never over-order almonds again."</p>
                <div class="proof-stat-row">
                    <div class="proof-stat">
                        <span class="proof-stat-num">200+</span>
                        <span class="proof-stat-label">bulk SKUs tracked</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="proof-stat">
                        <span class="proof-stat-num">kg</span>
                        <span class="proof-stat-label">decimal quantities</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="proof-stat">
                        <span class="proof-stat-num">14d</span>
                        <span class="proof-stat-label">free to try</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="sol-page">

    <div class="pains-section">
        <div class="pains-label">Sound familiar?</div>
        <div class="pains-grid">
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>Your POS only handles whole units — but you sell 0.35 kg of pistachios at a time</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>You don't know if a product is actually profitable until you've nearly sold through it</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>Supplier costs fluctuate and you lose track of what you paid last time you ordered</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pain-item">
                <div class="pain-icon">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p>Running a promotion on seasonal items means manually adjusting prices everywhere</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="solutions-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">How DMD handles bulk retail</h2>
        <div class="sol-cards">

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon amber-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 12h8M12 8v8"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Decimal quantities, built in</h3>
                <p>DMD's business type setting switches the entire platform to decimal mode. Sell 0.5 kg, 1.25 kg, or 3.7 kg — every transaction, report, and stock level reflects the exact weight you moved.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Decimal quantities</span>
                    <span class="tag">Weight-based stock</span>
                    <span class="tag">Business type setting</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon teal-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M6 2 3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4z"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Track what you paid, every time</h3>
                <p>Every purchase order records your cost per unit. DMD shows your last purchase cost inline when you reorder — so when your almond supplier raises prices by 8%, you see it immediately before confirming the PO.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Last purchase cost</span>
                    <span class="tag">Cost tracking</span>
                    <span class="tag">Purchase orders</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon green-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Know your margin on every product</h3>
                <p>Product profitability reports show you gross margin per SKU. Find out which varieties are worth your shelf space and which ones you're practically giving away. Adjust pricing or drop them entirely.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Product profitability</span>
                    <span class="tag">Margin analysis</span>
                    <span class="tag">Sales summary</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon navy-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M20 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Stock levels that actually reflect reality</h3>
                <p>Every gram sold reduces your stock. Every kilogram received adds to it. The movements log gives you an immutable record of every change — useful when a bin looks emptier than the system says it should be.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Live stock levels</span>
                    <span class="tag">Stock movements log</span>
                    <span class="tag">Manual adjustments</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon orange-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.82z"/><line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7.01" y2="7"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Seasonal promotions without the headache</h3>
                <p>Ramadan, Eid, holiday gifting — bulk shops run seasonal specials. Build a promotion in 3 steps, choose which products it applies to, set your discount, and it auto-applies at checkout for every staff member.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">Promotions wizard</span>
                    <span class="tag">Auto-apply</span>
                    <span class="tag">Print specials</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sol-card">
                <div class="sol-card-icon blue-icon">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Multi-language for your team</h3>
                <p>Many dry goods shops in Canada are run by multilingual teams. DMD runs in English, French, and Arabic — with full RTL support. Your staff works in the language they're most comfortable in.</p>
                <div class="sol-card-tags">
                    <span class="tag">English</span>
                    <span class="tag">French (CA)</span>
                    <span class="tag">Arabic + RTL</span>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explore-more">
        <h2>Also built for</h2>
        <div class="explore-grid">
            <a href="/solutions/retail" class="explore-card">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
                <div>
                    <div class="explore-name">Retail Stores</div>
                    <div class="explore-desc">General &amp; specialty retail</div>
                </div>
                <svg class="explore-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/solutions/restaurants" class="explore-card">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
                <div>
                    <div class="explore-name">Restaurants</div>
                    <div class="explore-desc">Table management &amp; kitchen flow</div>
                </div>
                <svg class="explore-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sol-cta">
        <h2>Ready to take control of your bulk inventory?</h2>
        <p>14-day free trial. No credit card. Set up in under an hour.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
            <a href="/contact?plan=drygoods" class="btn-primary">Start free trial</a>
            <a href="/features" class="btn-ghost">See all features</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<style>
    :root {
        --teal: #00BFA5;
        --teal-dark: #00897B;
        --teal-light: #E0F7F4;
        --navy: #1A237E;
        --navy-light: #E8EAF6;
        --text: #1C1C1E;
        --text-muted: #6B7280;
        --border: #E5E7EB;
        --surface: #F9FAFB;
        --white: #FFFFFF;
    }

    .sol-hero {
        background: #FFFFFF;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .sol-hero::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        right: -100px;
        bottom: -100px;
        width: 400px;
        height: 400px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245,158,11,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .sol-hero-inner {
        position: relative;
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .sol-eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        background: #FEF3C7;
        border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.25);
        color: #92400E;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.09em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 5px 12px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        width: fit-content;
    }

    .eyebrow-dot {
        width: 6px;
        height: 6px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #F59E0B;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .sol-title {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.12;
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    .sol-accent { color: #92400E; }

    .sol-sub {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    }

    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    .btn-primary {
        display: inline-block;
        background: var(--teal);
        color: #FFFFFF;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--teal-dark); }

    .btn-ghost {
        display: inline-block;
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--teal); color: var(--teal-dark); }

    .proof-card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .proof-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

    .proof-avatar {
        width: 42px;
        height: 42px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #FEF3C7;
        color: #92400E;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .proof-name { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
    .proof-role { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 1px; }

    .proof-quote {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.65;
        font-style: italic;
        border-left: 3px solid #F59E0B;
        padding-left: 0.875rem;
        margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .proof-stat-row {
        display: flex;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    .proof-stat {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2px;
        border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .proof-stat:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .proof-stat-num {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #92400E;
    }

    .proof-stat-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-align: center; }

    .sol-page { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem; }

    .pains-section {
        padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .pains-label {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #9CA3AF;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .pains-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .pain-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 10px;
        background: #FFF8F8;
        border: 1px solid #FEE2E2;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .pain-icon { color: #EF4444; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    .pain-item p { font-size: 0.825rem; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.55; margin: 0; }

    .section-heading {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text);
        margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    }

    .sol-cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .sol-card {
        background: var(--white);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .sol-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--teal);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,191,165,0.08);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .sol-card-icon {
        width: 44px;
        height: 44px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .teal-icon { background: var(--teal-light); color: var(--teal-dark); }
    .navy-icon { background: var(--navy-light); color: var(--navy); }
    .green-icon { background: #E8F5E9; color: #2E7D32; }
    .amber-icon { background: #FEF3C7; color: #92400E; }
    .orange-icon { background: #FFF3E0; color: #E65100; }
    .blue-icon { background: #E3F2FD; color: #1565C0; }

    .sol-card h3 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
    .sol-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 1rem; }

    .sol-card-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }

    .tag {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        padding: 3px 8px;
        border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .explore-more { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

    .explore-more h2 {
        font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text);
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    .explore-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .explore-card {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--text);
        transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }

    .explore-card:hover { border-color: var(--teal); background: var(--teal-light); }
    .explore-card svg:first-child { color: var(--teal-dark); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .explore-name { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
    .explore-desc { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2px; }
    .explore-arrow { margin-left: auto; color: var(--text-muted); flex-shrink: 0; }

    .sol-cta {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .sol-cta h2 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin: 0 0 0.6rem; }
    .sol-cta p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0 0 1.75rem; }
    .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    @@media (max-width: 700px) { .sol-hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; } }
    @@media (max-width: 640px) { .sol-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .pains-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
